OVERVIEW OF THE PROJECT
Objectives of the Project
Understand the Data:
1)Load the IMDb Movie Reviews dataset.
Perform exploratory data analysis (EDA) to understand the distribution of reviews, identify any data imbalances, and clean the data if necessary.
Data Preprocessing:
Data Preprocessing:
Preprocess the text data to make it suitable for model training.
Tokenize and pad the sequences to ensure uniform input size for the model.
Convert textual labels into numerical format.
Key Activities of the Project
1)Data Collection and Loading:
Obtain the IMDb Movie Reviews dataset from a reliable source.
Load the dataset into a pandas DataFrame for easy manipulation and analysis.
2)Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA):
Inspect the dataset to understand its structure, including the number of samples, feature types, and target distribution.
Visualize the distribution of positive and negative reviews.
Identify and handle missing or duplicate data.
